Subject: [PATCH v2 13/15] phy: qcom-qmp-combo: add support for updated sc8280xp binding
Date:   Tue, 15 Nov 2022 15:40:03 +0100
Message-Id: <20221115144005.2478-14-johan+linaro@kernel.org>
